  },
  {
    question: "Do callers actually text back?",
    answer: "A meaningful proportion do — particularly homeowners who have been noticing worsening condensation for months and want the problem fixed. Typical replies include the number of misted units, the frame type, the property address, and whether they want just the glass or full window replacement. These details arrive in your lead summary before you make the return call."
